      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver at a honest price? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs well and handles everyday commuting with ease! You'll notice some exterior wear like scratches and minor dents, and the interior shows signs of regular use, but mechanically it's holding its own. Priced fairly to reflect exactly what you're getting \u2014 a practical, functional vehicle without any surprises!",
