    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Here's your chance to own a truly exceptional vehicle in mint condition \u2014 and this one is the real deal! The exterior is flawless, with absolutely no scratches, dings, or blemishes to be found anywhere. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 clean, fresh, and well-maintained throughout. Under the hood, everything is running smoothly and performing exactly as it should. This is a rare find for buyers who want a car they can be proud of from day one. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations!",
      "price": 45500.0,
